headline: BofA raises Seagate, Western Digital targets on resilient pricing dynamics
summary: Investing.com -- Bank of America raised its price objectives on Seagate and Western Digital, citing stronger-than-expected hard disk drive (HDD) pricing and improved profitability outlooks.

headline: Bernstein Rates Seagate (STX) Outperform, HDD Rebound & HAMR Drive $250 PT
